title: "Breaking the Memory Wall: A Survey of Key-Value Cache Compression for Large Language Model Inference and the Matched-Budget Evaluation Protocol"
abstract: "Survey of KV cache compression for LLM inference, introducing the Matched-Budget Evaluation (MBE) protocol for standardized, fixed-budget reporting."
